{
  "texts": [
    "The researchers in (Jokar et al., 2015) implemented a pattern recognition technique based on unsupervised learning models for ETD in the data set of smart meters.",
    "The deployment of advanced sensors has strengthened the monitoring capability of power plants.",
    "In the context of the cogeneration process, the plant cooling is performed by the cooling towers using the condensation process on exhaust steam.",
    "However, the computer networks and industrial control systems built on this sensor-based digital layer may become vulnerable to cyber attacks.",
    "This may eventually raise a concern on the performance and security of these energy utilities."
  ]
}